var book = {
	"name": "Hebrifoɔ",
	"numChapters": 13,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Onyankopɔn a tete no ɔnam mmerɛ ahodoɔ ne akwan ahodoɔ so, nam adiyifoɔ so kasa kyerɛɛ agyanom no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> nna a ɛdi akyire yi mu nso, ɔnam Ɔba no so akasa akyerɛ yɛn. Ɔno na wayɛ no nnoɔma nyinaa ɔdedifoɔ, a ɔnam ne so nso abɔ wiase nyinaa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔno ara a ɔyɛ n’animuonyam no haran ne ne su nsɛsoɔ, na ɔde ne tumi asɛm sɔ nnoɔma nyinaa mu no, ɔde ɔno ara ne ho dwiraa yɛn bɔne no, ɔkɔtenaa animuonyam kɛseɛ no nifa so ɔsorosoro,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na wakyɛne abɔfoɔ no mmoroso, sɛdeɛ ne din kunini a wanya no kyɛne wɔn deɛ no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na abɔfoɔ mu hwan na waka akyerɛ no pɛn sɛ: Me ba ne wo, me na mawo wo nnɛ, na bio: Mɛyɛ no Agya, na ɔno nso ayɛ me ɔba?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔnya de abakan no ba wiase bio a, ɔse: Ma Nyankopɔn abɔfoɔ nyinaa nsɔre no!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na abɔfoɔ no ho deɛ, ɔse: Ɔyɛ n’abɔfoɔ mframa ne n’asomfoɔ, ogyaframa,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔba no ho deɛ, ɔse: Onyankopɔn, w’ahennwa wɔ hɔ daapem daapem, w’ahennie poma yɛ poma a ɛtene.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wodɔ tenenee, na wokyiri amumuyɛ enti na Onyankopɔn, wo Nyankopɔn, de ahosan ngo asra woɔ asene wo mfɛfoɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na: Awurade, mfitiaseɛ no, wotoo asase fapem, na wo nsa ano nnwuma ne ɔsoro.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yeinom bɛsɛe, nanso wo deɛ, wowɔ hɔ ara, na ne nyinaa bɛsu sɛ atadeɛ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wobɛbobɔ wɔn sɛ firatam, na wɔasakyera wɔn sɛ atadeɛ. Na wo deɛ, wote sɛ deɛ wote ara, na wo mfeɛ renhi da.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na abɔfoɔ no mu hwan ho na waka pɛn sɛ: Tena me nifa so kɔsi sɛ mede w’atamfo bɛyɛ wo nan ase ntiasoɔ?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wɔn nyinaa nyɛ ahonhom asomfoɔ a, wɔn a, wɔbɛyɛ nkwagyeɛ no adedifoɔ no nti, wɔsoma wɔn sɛ wɔnkɔsom no anaa?"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yei nti ɛsɛ sɛ yɛsɔ nnoɔma a yɛateɛ no mu den ma no boro soɔ, na yɛamfiri ho da bi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na sɛ asɛm a wɔnam abɔfoɔ so kaeɛ no timii, na mmarato ne asoɔden biara nyaa n’akatua a ɛsɛ a,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> yɛn nso, sɛ yɛammu nkwagyeɛ kɛseɛ a ɛte sɛ yei a, yɛbɛdwane afiri mu sɛn? Ɛno na Awurade firii aseɛ kaeɛ no, wɔn a wɔteeɛ no hyɛɛ mu den maa yɛn,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na Onyankopɔn nso de nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ ne ahoɔdenneɛ ahodoɔ ne Honhom Kronkron a ɔkyekyɛɛ mu sɛ ɔpɛ no dii ho adanseɛ bi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ ɛnyɛ abɔfoɔ ase na ɔde wiase a ɛreba a yɛka ho asɛm no ahyɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na obi di adanseɛ baabi sɛ: Ɔdasani ne hwan a wokae no, anaasɛ onipa ba ne hwan a w’ani ku ne ho?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Woama no aka kakraa bi na wato abɔfoɔ, wode animuonyam ne anidie abɔ no abotire, [na wode no asi wo nsa ano nnwuma so,]",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> wode nnoɔma nyinaa ahyɛ ne nan ase. Na sɛ ɔde nnoɔma nyinaa ahyɛ n’ase yi, wannya biribiara a wamfa anhyɛ n’aseɛ. Na seesei deɛ, yɛnnya nhunuu sɛ wɔde nnoɔma nyinaa ahyɛ n’ase.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mmom, yɛhunu Yesu, deɛ berɛ tiawa bi mu, wɔbrɛɛ no ase senee abɔfoɔ no, sɛdeɛ ɔbɛfa Onyankopɔn adom so bɛka owuo ahwɛ ama nnipa nyinaa. Seesei ɛsiane owuo amanehunu nti, wɔde animuonyam ne anidie abɔ no abotire.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɛfataa deɛ ne nti nnoɔma nyinaa wɔ hɔ na ɛnam ne so na nnoɔma nyinaa wɔ hɔ, deɛ ɔde mma bebree baa animuonyam mu no, sɛ ɔde wɔn nkwagyeɛ safohene nam amanehunu mu bɛkɔ pɛyɛ mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na deɛ ɔte yɛn ho ne wɔn a wɔate wɔn ho nyinaa wɔ abɔseɛ baako, ne saa nti ɛnyɛ no aniwu sɛ ɔbɛfrɛ wɔn anuanom,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> sɛ: Mɛbɔ wo din makyerɛ me nuanom, asafo mu na mɛto ayeyie dwom mama woɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na bio: Mede me ho bɛto ne so. Na bio nso: Hwɛ, me ne mma a Onyankopɔn de wɔn ama me no nie.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enti sɛ mma no anya honam ne mogya korɔ no bie no, saa ara na ɔno nso faa mu bi, sɛ ɔnam owuo so bɛtu deɛ ɔwɔ owuo tumi a ɔne ɔbonsam no,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na wagye wɔn a anka owuo ho hu nti wɔayɛ nkoa, nna a wɔde te aseɛ nyinaa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ampa ara, ɛnyɛ abɔfoɔ na ɔsɔ wɔn mu gye wɔn, na mmom Abraham asefoɔ na ɔsɔ wɔn mu gye wɔn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Enti ɛhiaa no sɛ ɔsɛ ne nuanom nnoɔma nyinaa mu, na wayɛ mmɔborɔhunu ne nokorɛ sɔfo panin, Nyankopɔn fam nnoɔma no mu, na wayɛ ɔman no bɔne ho mpata.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ ɔno ara hunuu sɔ a wɔsɔɔ no hwɛeɛ mu amaneɛ nti, ɔtumi boa wɔn a wɔsɔ wɔn hwɛ no."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛno nti, anuanom akronkronfoɔ a mofra ɔsoro frɛ no mu, monhwɛ yɛn asɛm a yɛgyina so ka no ho Ɔsomafoɔ ne Ɔsɔfo Panin Yesu",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> a ɔdi deɛ ɔde no sii hɔ no nokorɛ sɛdeɛ Mose nso dii Nyankopɔn fie nyinaa mu nokorɛ no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na oyi deɛ, wɔabu no sɛ animuonyam bebree sɛ no, sene Mose, te sɛ deɛ ɔsi efie wɔ anidie bebree sene efie no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> (Ɛfiri sɛ efie biara, obi na ɔsie, na deɛ ɔyɛɛ nnoɔma nyinaa ne Onyankopɔn.)",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Mose deɛ, ɔdii Nyankopɔn fie nyinaa mu nokorɛ sɛ ɔsomfoɔ, sɛ ɔbɛdi nsɛm a wɔrebɛka da bi no ho adanseɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Kristo deɛ, ɔdi ne fie so sɛ ɔba; nso ne fie no ne yɛn, nanso gye sɛ yɛsɔ anidasoɔ no ho nnam ne ahohoahoa mu pintinn kɔsi awieeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Enti, sɛdeɛ Honhom Kronkron ka no: Ɛnnɛ, sɛ mote ne nne a,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> mommpirim mo akoma sɛ atuateɛ no mu, sɔhwɛ da no wɔ serɛ so hɔ,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> deɛ mo agyanom gyegyee me hɔ no de sɔɔ me hwɛeɛ, na wɔhunuu me nnwuma mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti saa awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ yi ho yɛɛ me ahi, na mekaa sɛ: Wɔfom daa wɔ wɔn akoma mu. Nanso wɔn deɛ, wɔanhunu m’akwan;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> sɛdeɛ mekaa ntam wɔ m’abufuo mu no: Wɔrenhyɛne me home mu da.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Monhwɛ yie, anuanom, na akoma bɔne a ɛnnye nnie amma mo mu biara mu, na wanwae amfiri Onyankopɔn teasefoɔ ho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mmom montutu mo ho fo da biara a wɔda so bɔ din sɛ “ɛnnɛ” no, na bɔne nnaadaa ampirim mo mu biara akoma.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nanso sɛ deɛ yɛfirii aseɛ de yɛn ho too soɔ no, yɛsɔ mu pintinn kɔsi awieeɛ a, yɛn ne Kristo bɛyɛ baako.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ wɔka sɛ: Ɛnnɛ, sɛ mote ne nne a, mommpirim mo akoma sɛ ahiyie no mu a,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na ɛhefoɔ na wɔteeɛ a wɔtee atua no? Ɛnyɛ wɔn a wɔnam Mose so firii Misraim nyinaa no anaa?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛhefoɔ ho na ɛyɛɛ no ahi mfirinhyia aduanan no? Ɛnyɛ wɔn a wɔyɛɛ bɔne a wɔn amu guguu serɛ soɔ no anaa?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛhefoɔ na ɔkaa wɔn ntam sɛ wɔrenhyɛne n’ahome mu? Ɛnyɛ wɔn a wɔyɛɛ asoɔden no anaa?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na yɛhunu sɛ ɔgyeɛ a wɔannye annie nti, wɔantumi anhyɛn n’ahomegyeɛ no mu."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saa nti, ɛnam sɛ wɔagya yɛn ne home mu kɔ ho bɔhyɛ nti, momma yɛnsuro, na mo mu biara anyɛ sɛ waka akyi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔaka asɛmpa nso akyerɛ yɛn sɛ wɔn ara; nanso wɔannya asɛm a wɔteeɛ no ho mfasoɔ, ɛfiri sɛ ɛne gyidie no annkɔ bɛn korɔ mu, wɔn a wɔteeɛ no mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na yɛn a yɛagye adie no kɔ ɔhome no mu, sɛdeɛ ɔkaa sɛ: Mekaa ntam m’abufuo mu sɛ: Wɔrenhyɛne me home mu. Nanso wɔfiri wiase fapemtoɔ awie nnwuma no dada.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na baabi waka ɛda a ɛtɔ so nson no ho asɛm sɛ: Na Onyankopɔn homee da a ɛtɔ so nson firi ne nnwuma nyinaa mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛhanom ɔka bio sɛ: Wɔrenhyɛne me home mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Enti, sɛ aka sɛ ebinom bɛkɔ mu, na asoɔden nti wɔn a wɔkaa wɔn asɛmpa no kane no ankɔ mu nti,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ɔhyɛɛ da bi bio nam Dawid so kaa sɛ: “Ɛnnɛ”, ɛkyɛree saa no, ɔkaa sɛdeɛ yɛabɔ din dada no sɛ: Ɛnnɛ, sɛ mote ne nne a, mommpirim mo akoma!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ na Yosua ama wɔn ahome a, anka akyire yi wammɔ da foforɔ din bio.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnneɛ na homedadie da so ara wɔ hɔ ma Nyankopɔn man.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na deɛ wahyɛne ne home mu no, ɔno nso home firii ne nnwuma ho, sɛdeɛ Onyankopɔn home firii ne deɛ ho no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Enti momma yɛmmɔ mmɔden nhyɛne ɔhome no mu, na obi anhwe ase anyɛ asoɔden korɔ no ara ho nhwɛsoɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Nyankopɔn asɛm wɔ nkwa, na ahoɔden wɔ mu, na ano yɛ nnam sene nkrantɛ anofanu biara, na ɛhwire mu kɔduru sɛ ɛpaepae ɔkra ne honhom, akwaa ne ekyim mu, na ɛyɛ akoma nsusuiɛ ne adwene temmufoɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na abɔdeɛ biara nni hɔ a ɛnna adie Nyankopɔn anim, na ade nyinaa ho da hɔ, na ɛso abue, deɛ yɛne no wɔ asɛm no anim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enti, sɛ yɛwɔ ɔsɔfo panin kɛseɛ a watwa mu ɔsoro, a ɔno ne Yesu, Nyankopɔn Ba no yi, momma yɛnsɔ yɛn gyidie asɛm a yɛgyina so ka no mu dendeenden.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na yɛnni ɔsɔfo panin a ɔnnim yɛn mmerɛyɛ na ɔnni tema mma yɛn, na mmom deɛ wɔasɔ no ahwɛ adeɛ nyinaa mu sɛ yɛn ara, nso wannyɛ bɔne.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Enti momma yɛmfa nnam mmra adom ahennwa no anim, na yɛanya mmɔborɔhunu, na yɛahunu adom, na ɛberɛ a ɛsɛ mu aboa yɛn."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔsɔfo panin biara, wɔyi no firi nnipa mu hyɛ no sɔfoɔ ma nnipa, Nyankopɔn fam nnoɔma ho, na bɔne nti, ɔde ayɛyɛdeɛ ne afɔdeɛ ama,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> sɛ obi a ɔbɛtumi ahunu ama wɔn a wɔnnim na wɔfom no, ɛsiane sɛ mmerɛyɛ atwa ɔno nso ho ahyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɛno nti, ɛsɛ sɛ ɔbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ma ne ho, sɛdeɛ ɔbɔ ma ɔman no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na obi mfa saa anidie no mma ne ho, gye sɛ deɛ Onyankopɔn afrɛ no te sɛ Aaron no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Saa ara nso na Kristo anhyɛ ne ho animuonyam sɛ ɔbɛyɛ ɔsɔfo panin, na mmom deɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Me ba ne wo, me na mawo wo nnɛ!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sɛdeɛ ɔkaa no baabi nso sɛ: Woyɛ daa sɔfo, wɔ Melkisedek kwan so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɔno a ne honam nna no mu ɔde mpaebɔ ne nkotosrɛ brɛɛ deɛ ɔbɛtumi agye no afiri owuo mu wɔ nteamu a emu yɛ den ne nisuo mu, na ahobrɛaseɛ suro nti wɔtiee no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɔyɛ Ɔba deɛ, nanso ɔsuaa amaneɛ a ɔhunuiɛ no mu setie,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔnya dii mu no, ɔyɛɛ wɔn a wɔyɛ setie ma no no nyinaa daa nkwagyeɛ farebae,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> a Onyankopɔn bɔ ne din frɛ no ɔsɔfo panin wɔ Melkisedek kwan so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛno ho na yɛwɔ nsɛm pii a asekyerɛ yɛ den, nanso mo aso asisi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛberɛ a anka ɛsɛ sɛ moyɛ akyerɛkyerɛfoɔ no, ɛhia mo bio sɛ wɔkyerɛkyerɛ mo Nyankopɔn nsɛm mu mfitiasesɛm, na moayɛ sɛ wɔn a ɛhia wɔn nufosuo, na ɛnyɛ aduane a ɛyɛ den.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na obiara a ɔnum nufoɔ no nhunuu tenenee asɛm no mu, na ɔyɛ akɔkoaa.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na aduane a ɛyɛ den no fata wɔn a wɔanyini a ɛnam daa daa adeyɛ nti wɔn adwene tumi hunu papa ne bɔne mu."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Enti momma yɛmfa mfitiaseɛ nkyerɛkyerɛ a ɛfa Kristo ho no nto nkyɛn, na yɛmpere nkɔ deɛ ɛyɛ pɛ no mu, na yɛamfa nnwuma funu mu adwensakyera ne Nyankopɔn ho gyidie",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ne asubɔ ahodoɔ ho nkyerɛkyerɛ ne nsagusoɔ ne awufoɔ sɔreɛ ne daa atemmuo anto fapem bio.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Yei na sɛ Onyankopɔn ma ho kwan a, yɛbɛyɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɛntumi mma sɛ, wɔn a wɔanya hann pɛn, na wɔaka ɔsoro akyɛdeɛ no ahwɛ, na wɔanya Honhom Kronkron no bie,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na wɔaka Nyankopɔn asɛm a ɛyɛ ne wiase a ɛrebɛba no ahoɔden ahodoɔ ahwɛ,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na wɔafiri ho ahwe aseɛ no, wɔbɛdane wɔn foforɔ akɔ adwensakyera mu, wɔn a wɔsɛne Nyankopɔn Ba no bio ma wɔn ho na wɔde no kɔ animguaseɛ mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na asase a ɛnom osuo a ɛtaa tɔ gu soɔ na ɛfifiri aduane a ɛyɛ ma wɔn a wɔn nti wɔdɔ no, nya Nyankopɔn hɔ nhyira no bi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na deɛ ɛfifiri nkasɛɛ ne hwerɛmo no, ɛmfra, na ɛbɛn nnuabɔ a n’awieeɛ ne ɔhyeɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ yɛka saa nso a, adɔfo, mo fam deɛ, yɛn ani da deɛ ɛyɛ sene saa a ɛbata nkwagyeɛ ho so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn nyɛ deɛ ɔntene, a ne werɛ bɛfiri mo adwuma ne mo dɔ mmɔden a mobɔɔ no ne din mu, sɛ mosomm ahotefoɔ na moda so som wɔn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na yɛyi yɛn yam pɛ sɛ mo nyinaa mmaako mmaako yi saa mmɔdemmɔ yi adi kyerɛ wɔ anidasoɔ a akyinnyeɛ nni mu koraa mu de kɔduru awieeɛ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na moanyɛ nyaa, na mmom moayɛ wɔn a wɔnam gyidie ne abodwokyɛre so nyaa bɔhyɛ no asuafoɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Onyankopɔn hyɛɛ Abraham bɔ no, na ɔnni deɛ ɔso sene no a ɔbɛka ne ntam nti, ɔkaa ɔno ara ne ho ntam",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> sɛ: Ampa ara, nhyira na mɛhyira woɔ, na dɔre na mɛma woadɔre.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔtoo ne bo ase twɛnee saa no, ne nsa kaa bɔhyɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ nnipa ka deɛ ɔso sene wɔn ntam, na ntuatuaano nyinaa to twa ne ntanka a wɔde hyɛ asɛm mu den.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛno nti na Onyankopɔn pɛɛ sɛ ɔyi n’atirimusɛm a ɛnsakyera kyerɛ bɔhyɛ no adedifoɔ pefee no, ɔde ntam gyinaa mu,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na yɛafa nnoɔma mmienu a ɛnsakyera, a ɛkyerɛ sɛ Onyankopɔn nni atorɔ wɔ biribiara mu no so anya awerɛhyɛmu a emu yɛ den, na yɛn a yɛadwane repɛ hintabea no bɛsɔ anidasoɔ a ɛda yɛn anim no mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛno na yɛwɔ sɛ ɔkra sɛkyɛ a ɛnteɛ, na ɛtim hɔ a ɛhyɛne mu de kɔsi ntwamutam no mu,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> deɛ odikanfoɔ bi hyɛnee hɔ maa yɛn no, ɔno ne Yesu a wayɛ Melkisedek kwan so daa sɔfo panin."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na saa Melkisedek yi, Salem hene, Ɔsorosoro Nyankopɔn sɔfoɔ, Abraham kɔkumm ahene no na ɔresane aba no, ɔkɔhyiaa no hyiraa no.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nso Abraham maa no ade nyinaa so ntotosoɔ du du, ɛkyerɛ sɛ ɔyɛ tenenee hene kane, na ɛno akyiri nso, ɔyɛ Salem hene, ɛne asomdwoeɛ hene,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ɔnni agya nni na nni awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ, ɔnni nna mfitiaseɛ anaa nkwa awieeɛ, na wɔde no toto Nyankopɔn Ba no ho a, ɔyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ afebɔɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na monhwɛ onipa yi a agya panin Abraham maa no asadeɛ no so ntotosoɔ du du no so a ɔso!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔn a wɔfiri Lewi mma mu nya asɔfodwuma no nso wɔ ahyɛdeɛ bi sɛ wɔnnye ntotosoɔ du du, sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ, wɔ ɔman no mu, ɛne sɛ, wɔn nuanom a wɔn nso wɔfiri Abraham asene mu no, nkyɛn,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> nanso deɛ n’abusua mfiri wɔn mu no gyee Abraham hɔ ntotosoɔ du du, na ɔhyiraa deɛ ɔwɔ bɔhyɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso akyinnyeɛ biara nni mu sɛ deɛ ɔkyɛne soɔ no na ɔhyira akumaa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɛha, nnipa a wɔwuo na wɔgye ntotosoɔ du du, na ɛhɔ deɛ, deɛ wɔdi ne ho adanseɛ sɛ ɔte aseɛ no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na yɛbɛtumi aka sɛ, Lewi nso a ɔgye ntotosoɔ du du no nam Abraham so maa ntotosoɔ du du no bi,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ɛfiri sɛ berɛ a Melkisedek bɛhyiaa no no, na ɔda so wɔ n’agya asene mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na afei sɛ pɛyɛ nam Lewifoɔ asɔfodie so ba a, (ɛfiri sɛ ɛno so na ɔman no nyaa mmara no,) anka ɛdeɛn hia na ɛhia bio sɛ Melkisedek akwan so sɔfoɔ foforɔ bɛsɔreɛ na wɔnka no sɛ Aaron kwan soɔ?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ wɔsakyeraa asɔfodie no a, ɛtwa sɛ wɔsakyera mmara no nso.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na deɛ wɔbɔ ne din ka nsɛm yi firi abusuakuo foforɔ a obi mfiri mu mmɛyɛɛ afɔrebukyia ho adwuma pɛn mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ ɛda adi pefee sɛ, Yuda mu na yɛn Awurade pueeɛ, nso saa abusuakuo yi, Mose ammɔ din anka asɔfodie ho hwee.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na deɛ ɛma asɛm no da adi pefee koraa ne sɛ, ɔsɔfoɔ foforɔ sɔre Melkisedek nsɛsoɔ so",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> a wɔamfa honam ahyɛdeɛ mmara so, na mmom wɔnam nkwa a ɛnsɛeɛ ahoɔden so ayɛ no ɔsɔfoɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔdi ne ho adanseɛ sɛ: Woyɛ Melkisedek kwan so sɔfoɔ daa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔgu ahyɛdeɛ bi a ɛdi kan wɔ emu adeɛ a ɛyɛ mmerɛ na ɛho nni mfasoɔ nti,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> (ɛfiri sɛ mmara no amma biribiara anni mu), nanso wɔde anidasoɔ a ɛyɛ kyɛne soɔ a yɛnam so bɛn Onyankopɔn ba mu, de si ananmu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na sɛdeɛ wɔankwati ntanka anyɛ yei no, ɛwom sɛ wɔn deɛ, wɔkwatii ntanka yɛɛ asɔfoɔ,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> nanso oyi deɛ, deɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Awurade aka ntam na ɔrennu ne ho sɛ: Woyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ daa no, de ntanka ahyɛ no sɔfoɔ,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> sɛdeɛ apam a Yesu adi mu agyinamu yi yɛ kyɛne soɔ ne no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, ɛsiane sɛ owuo amma wɔantena hɔ nti, wɔyɛɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔdɔɔso,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> nanso oyi deɛ, ɛnam sɛ ɔte hɔ daa nti, ɔdi sɔfoɔ afebɔɔ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Saa nti, ɔbɛtumi agye wɔn a wɔnam ne so ba Nyankopɔn nkyɛn no koraa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔte ase daa sɛ ɔbɛdi ama wɔn.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔsɔfo panin a ɔfata yɛn ne saa ɔsɔfo panin yi a ne ho teɛ, ɔnni bɔne, ne ho nni nkekaeɛ, wɔayi no afiri nnebɔneyɛfoɔ ho, na wɔama no so akyɛne soro.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔno na ɛnhia no daa, sɛ asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ no, sɛ ɔbɔ ɔno ara ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ kane ansa na wabɔ ɔman no deɛ, na mmom ɔde ne ho bɔɔ afɔdeɛ no, ɔyɛɛ yei prɛko pɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na mmara no deɛ, ɛhyɛ nnipa a wɔyɛ mmerɛ asɔfoɔ mpanin, nanso mmara no akyiri ntanka asɛm no hyɛ ɔba a wawie pɛyɛ daa no sɔfo panin."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na nsɛm a yɛreka yi mu titire nie: Yɛwɔ saa ɔsɔfo panin a wakɔtena tumi kɛseɛ ahennwa no nifa, ɔsoro",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> sɛ kronkronbea ne nokorɛ ntomadan a Awurade no ara, na ɛnyɛ onipa, pameeɛ no mu sɔfoɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔsɔfo panin biara wɔhyɛ no sɛ ɔmfa ayɛyɛdeɛ ne afɔdeɛ mma, enti ɛsɛ sɛ oyi nso nya biribi a ɔde bɛma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na sɛ ɔwɔ asase so deɛ a, anka ɔnyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ mpo, ɛfiri sɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔde ayɛyɛdeɛ ma, sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ, wɔ hɔ dada.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Wɔn na wɔsom ɔsoro nnoɔma nhwɛsoɔ ne mfonini, te sɛdeɛ asɛm a berɛ a Mose rebɛsiesie ntomadan no, ɛbaa ne nkyɛn a ɛse: Hwɛ, yɛ adeɛ nyinaa sɛdeɛ nsususoɔ a wɔkyerɛɛ wo bepɔ no soɔ no teɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na afei ne nsa aka asɔfodwuma a ɛkyɛne soɔ, sɛ wayɛ apam a ɛkyɛne soɔ a wɔgyina bɔhyɛ a ɛkyɛne soɔ so hyɛɛ ho mmara no ntamgyinafoɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ kane apam no ho nni asɛm a, anka wɔrenhwehwɛ deɛ ɛtɔ so mmienu toberɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔnunu wɔn sɛ: Hwɛ, nna bi reba, Awurade na ɔseɛ, sɛ me ne Israel fie ne Yuda fie bɛpam apam foforɔ,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> ɛnte sɛ apam a me ne wɔn agyanom pameeɛ da a mesosɔɔ wɔn nsa meyii wɔn mefirii Misraim asase soɔ no; ɛfiri sɛ wɔn deɛ, wɔantena m’apam mu, na me nso mannwene wɔn ho, Awurade na ɔseɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na yei ne apam a nna no akyi me ne Israel fie bɛpam no, Awurade na ɔseɛ: Mede me mmara bɛhyɛ wɔn adwene mu, na matwerɛ no wɔn akoma mu, na mayɛ wɔn Nyankopɔn, na wɔn nso ayɛ me ɔman.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na obi renkyerɛkyerɛ ne kuromani, obi renkyerɛkyerɛ ne nua sɛ: Hunu Awurade! Na wɔn nyinaa bɛhunu me afiri wɔn mu akumaa so akɔsi ɔkɛseɛ so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mɛdom wɔn amumuyɛ ho, na wɔn bɔne deɛ, merenkae bio.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Deɛ ɔka sɛ “foforɔ” yi no, ɔde ayɛ kane deɛ no dada, na deɛ ɛreyɛ dada na ɛretwa mu no, aka kakra na ayera."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afei, kane apam no nso wɔ ɔsom ho nhyehyɛɛ ne wiase ha kronkronbea deɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ, wɔsii ntomadan bi a wɔkɔ mu kane a kaneadua ne ɛpono ne paanoo a ɛgu soɔ wɔ mu a wɔfrɛ hɔ kronkronbea.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ntwamutam a ɛtɔ so mmienu no mu wɔ ntomadan a wɔfrɛ hɔ kronkron mu kronkron.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛwɔ sika aduhwamhyeɛ bukyia ne apam adaka a wɔde sika adura ho nyinaa, a sika pɔre a mana wɔ mu, ne Aaron poma a ɛfefɛeɛ ne apam aboɔpono no wɔ mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛso na animuonyam Kerubim a ɛtrɛ mpata adwa no soɔ sie; nso yɛrentumi nka nnoɔma yi ho nsɛm mmaako mmaako seesei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔsiesiee nnoɔma yi saa a, asɔfoɔ no kɔ ntomadan a wɔsi mu kane no mu daa kɔyɛ ɔsom ho nnwuma.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na deɛ ɛtɔ so mmienu no deɛ, ɔsɔfo panin nko na afe biara ɔkɔ hɔ prɛko, ɔde mogya a ɔno ara, ne ɔman no mfomsoɔ nti ɔde kɔma.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Emu na Honhom Kronkron kyerɛ yei pefee sɛ, ɛberɛ a wɔnnya nyii kwan a ɛde kɔ kronkron mu no adi nkyerɛeɛ no, na ntomadan a ɛdi kan no da so si hɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛno yɛ mfatoho de ma seesei berɛ yi, sɛdeɛ wɔde ayɛyɛdeɛ nso ma, ɛne afɔdeɛ a ɛntumi mma deɛ ɔsom no nni mu n’ahonim fam,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na ɛne nnuane ne anonneɛ ne adware ahodoɔ yɛ honam nsiesieeɛ nko a ɛda hɔ sɛ wɔnyɛ nkɔduru berɛ a wɔahyɛ ato hɔ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nanso Kristo a ɔbaa sɛ nnepa a aba dada no ho sɔfo panin, nam ntomadan a ɛso na ɛyɛ pɛ kyɛne soɔ, (a wɔamfa nsa ansie, ɛne sɛ, ɛmfiri adebɔ yi mu mu),",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nso ɛnyɛ mmirekyie ne anantwie mma mogya, na mmom ɔno ara ne mogya so na ɔnam kɔɔ kronkronbea hɔ prɛko kɔnyaa daa ɔgyeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ mmirekyie ne anantwinini mogya ne nantwibereɛ nso a wɔde dwira wɔn a wɔn ho agu fi, te wɔn ho kɔ honam ahofire mu a,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> mprɛ ahe ara na Kristo a ɔnam daa honhom so de ne ho bɔɔ afɔdeɛ, a ɛho nni dɛm maa Onyankopɔn no mogya rente mo ahonim ho mfiri nnwuma funu mu nkɔsom Onyankopɔn a ɔte aseɛ?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Yei nti na ɔyɛ Apam foforɔ ntamgyinafoɔ, sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔn a wɔabɔ wɔn din afrɛ wɔn no anya daa agyapadeɛ bɔhyɛ no, ɛsiane owuo a ɔwu de gyee wɔn a wɔyɛɛ kane apam no ho mfomsoɔ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na deɛ samanseɛ wɔ no, ɛhɔ na ɛtwa sɛ wɔkyerɛ sɛ, deɛ ɔhyɛeɛ no awu,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na samanseɛ tim wɔ awufoɔ so, na deɛ ɔhyɛeɛ no te ase a, anka emu nyɛ den da.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛno nti na wɔankwati mogya anhyɛ kane apam no nso aseɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Mose kaa ahyɛdeɛ biara kyerɛɛ ɔman mu no nyinaa, sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ wieeɛ no, ɔfaa anantwie mma ne mmirekyie mogya ne nsuo ne kuntu kɔkɔɔ ne sommɛ na ɔde petee nwoma no ara ne ɔman no nyinaa so",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kaa sɛ: Yei ne apam a Onyankopɔn ahyɛ wɔ mo ho no mogya.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ntomadan ne asɔfodwuma nnoɔma nyinaa nso, ɔde mogya no petee ho saa ara.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ampa ara, wɔde mogya na ɛte nnoɔma nyinaa ho, sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ, na mogya angu a, bɔne fakyɛ nni hɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛnneɛ na ɛtwa sɛ wɔde yeinom te ɔsoro nnoɔma nhwɛsoɔ no ho. Na ɔsoro nnoɔma no ankasa deɛ, wɔde afɔdeɛ a ɛyɛ kyɛne yeinom na ɛtee ho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Kristo anhyɛne kronkronbea a wɔde nsa yɛeɛ, a ɛyɛ kronkronbea pa ara no ho nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ no mu, na mmom ɔhyɛnee ɔsoro ankasa sɛ afei ɔrekɔyi ne ho adi Nyankopɔn anim ama yɛn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nanso wanhyɛne hɔ sɛ ɔde ne ho bɛbɔ afɔdeɛ mprɛ pii, sɛdeɛ ɔsɔfo panin de obi mogya hyɛne kronkronbea daa mfirinhyia no;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ɛnneɛ anka ɛsɛ no sɛ ɔtaa hunu amane firi wiase fapem, na afei a wiase mmerɛ rewie duro yi, wayi ne ho adi prɛko sɛ ɔnam afɔdeɛ a ɔde ne ho bɔeɛ so bɛyi bɔne.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na sɛdeɛ ɛda hɔ ma nnipa sɛ wɔbɛwu prɛko na ɛno akyi atemmuo bɛba no,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> saa ara nso na Kristo a wɔde no bɔɔ afɔdeɛ prɛko sɛ ɔnsoa nnipa bebree bɔne no bɛkwati bɔne ayi ne ho adi ne mprenu soɔ, akyerɛ wɔn a wɔhwɛ no kwan no, de wɔn akɔ nkwagyeɛ mu."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ mmara no kura nnepa a ɛbɛba no nhwɛsoɔ na ɛnyɛ nnoɔma no suban ankasa nti, ɛntumi mfa afɔdeɛ korɔ no ara a wɔbobɔɔ no afe afe nyɛ wɔn a wɔbɔ no pɛ da;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na sɛ asɔrefoɔ a wɔate wɔn ho prɛko nni bɔne ho ahonim bio a, anka wɔannyae afɔrebɔ anaa?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na mmom bɔne ho nkaeɛ wɔ mu daa afirinhyia,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> ɛfiri sɛ anantwinini ne mmirekyie mogya ntumi nyi bɔne mfiri hɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Enti ɔreba wiase no, na ɔkaa sɛ: Afɔdeɛ ne ayɛyɛdeɛ, woampɛ, ɔhonam na woasiesie de ama me.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ansɔ w’ani.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛno na mekaa sɛ: Hwɛ, mereba, wɔatwerɛ me ho asɛm wɔ nwoma mmobɔeɛ no mu sɛ, merebɛyɛ deɛ wo, Onyankopɔn, wopɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kane no, ɔkaa sɛ: Afɔdeɛ ne ayɛyɛdeɛ ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, woampɛ, nanso ansɔ w’ani, (ɛne deɛ wɔnam mmara so de ma).",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛno na ɔkaa sɛ: Hwɛ, maba sɛ merebɛyɛ deɛ wopɛ; ɔyi deɛ ɛdi kan no hɔ, na ɔde deɛ ɛtɔ so mmienu no asi hɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Saa ɔpɛ no mu na wɔnam Yesu Kristo honam a ɔde bɛmaeɛ no soɔ ate yɛn ho prɛko.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ biara gyina hɔ daa resom, na ɔtaa bɔ afɔdeɛ korɔ no ara a ɛntumi nyi bɔne mfiri hɔ da.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔno deɛ, ɔnya bɔɔ daa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ baako no, ɔkɔtenaa Nyankopɔn nifa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na deɛ aka ne sɛ ɔtwɛn kɔduru sɛ wɔde n’atamfo bɛyɛ ne nan ase ntiasoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔde afɔdeɛ korɔ no ara ama wɔn a wɔate wɔn ho no awie pɛyɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Honhom Kronkron nso di yɛn adanseɛ. Ɛfiri sɛ akane no, ɔkaa sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yei ne apam a nna no akyi me ne wɔn bɛpam no, Awurade na ɔseɛ: Mede me mmara bɛhyɛ wɔn akoma mu, na matwerɛ wɔ wɔn adwene mu",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɔka toa so sɛ, na wɔn bɔne ne wɔn mmarato nso merenkae bio.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na deɛ yeinom fakyɛ wɔ no, bɔne ho afɔrebɔ nni hɔ bio.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti, anuanom, sɛ yɛwɔ Yesu mogya mu nnamyɛ a yɛde bɛkɔ kronkronbea hɔ,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ɛsiane ɔkwan a wɔsiesie ama yɛn, ɔkwan foforɔ a ɛwɔ nkwa a ɛfa ntwamutam, ɛne sɛ ne honam mu,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ne sɛ yɛwɔ Nyankopɔn fie so sɔfoɔ kɛseɛ nti,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> momma yɛmfa nokorɛ akoma wɔ gyidie a akyinnyeɛ nni mu koraa mmɛn sɛ nnipa a wɔapete wɔn akoma ho afiri ahonim bɔne mu, na wɔde nsuo korɔgyenn adware wɔn nipadua.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Momma yɛnsɔ anidasoɔ asɛm a yɛgyina so ka no mu pintinn, ɛfiri sɛ ɔnokwafoɔ ne deɛ ɔhyɛɛ bɔ no,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na momma yɛnhwehwɛ yɛn ho ntwetwe yɛn ho yɛn ho nkɔ ɔdɔ ne nnwuma pa mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mommma yɛnnnyae yɛn ho yɛn ho nhyiamu, sɛdeɛ ebinom yɛ no, na mmom momma yɛntutu yɛn ho yɛn ho fo, berɛ dodoɔ a mohunu sɛ Ɛda no rebɛn.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na sɛ yɛnya nya nokorɛ no mu nimdeɛ, na akyire yi yɛboapa kɔyɛ bɔne a, na bɔne ho afɔdeɛ biara nni hɔ bio,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na mmom deɛ aka ne atemmuo akwanhwɛ a ɛyɛ hu bi, ne ogya a ɛrebɛhye atamfoɔ no pasaa.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Sɛ obi to Mose mmara a, ɔkwati mmɔborɔhunu gyina adansefoɔ baanu anaa baasa anomu asɛm so wu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Akatua a ɛnyɛ koraa bɛn na mususu sɛ ɛsɛ sɛ wɔde bɛtua deɛ watiatia Nyankopɔn Ba no soɔ, na wabu apam mogya a wɔde ate ne ho no ahuhudeɛ, na wasopa adom honhom no?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na yɛnim deɛ ɔkaa sɛ: Me na aweretɔ wɔ me, me na mɛtua ka. Na bio: Awurade bɛbu ne man atɛn.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Onyankopɔn a ɔte aseɛ no nsa mu hweɛ yɛ hu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na monkae sɛ kane nna a monyaa hann no, momiaa mo ani hunuu ɔko bebree mu amane.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ebi ne sɛ, monam ahohora ne ahohia so yɛɛ adwasodeɛ, ebi nso ne sɛ moyɛɛ wɔn a wɔyɛɛ wɔn saa no mfɛfoɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na momaa nneduafoɔ amaneɛ kaa mo, mode anigyeɛ nso penee mo nnoɔma fom sɛ monim sɛ mowɔ ahodeɛ a ɛyɛ kyɛne soɔ ɔsoro a ɛtena hɔ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Enti monnto mo nnamyɛ a ɛwɔ akatua kɛseɛ no nntwene.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na boasetɔ hia mo, na sɛ mowie deɛ Onyankopɔn pɛ no yɛ a, mo nsa aka bɔhyɛ no.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na aka kakraa bi na deɛ ɔbɛba no aba, na ɔrenkyɛ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na deɛ ɔtene no firi gyidie mu bɛnya nkwa, na sɛ ɔtwe ne ho a, me kra ani rensɔ no.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na yɛn deɛ, yɛmfra wɔn a wɔtwe wɔn ho kɔ ɔsɛeɛ mu mu, na mmom yɛfra wɔn a wɔgye die na wɔkɔ nkwagyeɛ mu mu."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afei gyidie ne adeɛ a yɛn ani da soɔ ho ahotosoɔ ne nnoɔma a yɛnhunu ho adansegyeɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na yei mu na tetefoɔ no nyaa adanseɛ pa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Gyidie na yɛde te aseɛ sɛ wiase ahodoɔ wɔde Nyankopɔn asɛm na ɛsiesieeɛ, enti deɛ ani tua firi nnoɔma a ɛnna adie mu na ɛbaeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Gyidie na Habel de bɔɔ afɔdeɛ a ɛso kyɛne Kain deɛ maa Onyankopɔn. Ɛno so na ɔnam nyaa adanseɛ sɛ ɔtene, ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn dii n’ayɛyɛdeɛ ho adanseɛ, na ɛno so na sɛ ɔwui mpo a, ɔda so kasa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Gyidie nti na wɔfaa Henok kɔeɛ na wanhunu owuo; na wɔanhu no, ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn bɛfaa no kɔeɛ ntira; na ansa na wɔrebɛfa no akorɔ no, ɔnyaa adanseɛ sɛ ɔsɔ Nyankopɔn ani.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ gyidie nni mu a, obi ntumi nsɔ ani. Na ɛsɛ deɛ ɔba Nyankopɔn nkyɛn no sɛ, ɔgye di sɛ ɔwɔ hɔ, na ɔyɛ wɔn a wɔhwehwɛ n’akyiri kwan no katuafoɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Gyidie na deɛ wɔnnya nhunuu ɛho nsɛm baa Noa nkyɛn no, ɔde daa ne ho so siesiee adaka maa ne fie nkwagyeɛ, ɛno so na ɔnam buu wiase fɔ, na ɔyɛɛ gyidie ho tenenee ɔdedifoɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Gyidie na wɔfrɛɛ Abraham no, ɔde setie firi kɔɔ baabi a daakye ɔbɛnya hɔ sɛ agyapadeɛ, na ɔfirii adi a na ɔnnim deɛ ɔrekorɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Gyidie na ɔde kɔyɛɛ ɔhɔhoɔ bɔhyɛ asase no so, sɛ ananafoɔ deɛ soɔ, na ɔne bɔhyɛ korɔ no ara adedifoɔ Isak ne Yakob tenaa ntomadan mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔtwɛn kuro a ɛwɔ fapem a ne kyekyefoɔ ne yɛfoɔ ne Onyankopɔn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Gyidie na Sara nso de nyaa ahoɔden nyinsɛneeɛ, ɛberɛ a watra ne nyini mu, ɛfiri sɛ ɔbuu deɛ ɔhyɛɛ bɔ no nokwafoɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Enti nso na ɔbaako a ɔwuiɛ mpo woo nnipa a wɔdɔɔso sɛ ɔsoro nsoromma ne mpoano anwea a wɔntumi nkan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Gyidie so na yeinom nyinaa wuwuiɛ a wɔn nsa anka bɔhyɛ no, na mmom wɔhunuu akyirikyiri nko gye diiɛ, yɛɛ no atuu kaa sɛ, wɔyɛ ahɔhoɔ ne amamfrafoɔ wɔ asase so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔn a wɔka saa no, wɔde kyerɛ sɛ wɔhwehwɛ kuro bi a ɛbɛyɛ wɔn ara wɔn dea.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ wɔn akoma da deɛ wɔfiri mu baeɛ no so a, anka wɔwɔ akwannya sɛ wɔbɛsane akɔ hɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afei wɔrehwehwɛ kuro a ɛyɛ kyɛne soɔ a ɛne ɔsoro deɛ. Enti ɛnyɛ Onyankopɔn aniwu sɛ wɔbɛfrɛ no wɔn Nyankopɔn, ɛfiri sɛ wasiesie kuro bi ama wɔn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Gyidie nti na wɔsɔɔ Abraham hwɛeɛ no, ɔde Isak kɔbɔɔ afɔdeɛ, na deɛ ɔgyee bɔhyɛ no, de ne ba korɔ no kɔmae.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɔno na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Isak mu na wɔbɛfrɛ w’asefoɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɔsusuu sɛ Onyankopɔn bɛtumi anyane no afiri awufoɔ mu mpo. Ɛhɔ nso na ɔnyaa no bio, akasabebuo mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Gyidie na Isak de hyiraa Yakob ne Esau, nnoɔma a ɛbɛba ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Gyidie na Yakob rebɛwuo no, ɔde hyiraa Yosef mma baanu no, na ɔmiaa ne pomatire so sɔree.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Gyidie na Yosef regyae ne honhom mu no, ɔde bɔɔ Israel mma fire a wɔrebɛfiri akɔ no din, na ɔhyɛɛ ne nnompe ho samanseɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Gyidie na wɔwoo Mose no, n’awofoɔ de koraa no abosome mmiɛnsa, ɛfiri sɛ wɔhunuu sɛ abɔfra no ho yɛ fɛ, na wɔansuro ɔhene mmara no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Gyidie nti na Mose nyiniiɛ no, wampɛ sɛ wɔfrɛ no Farao babaa ba,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na ɔyii sɛ ɔne Nyankopɔn man bɛhunu amane mmom kyɛne sɛ ɔbɛte bɔne mu dɛ nna tiaa bie.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɔbuu Kristo ahohora sɛ ahonya kɛseɛ senee Misraim ahonyadeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ɔhwɛɛ akatua no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Gyidie nti na ɔgyaa Misraim hɔ, na wansuro ɔhene abufuo, na mmom ɔmiaa n’ani tenaa mu sɛdeɛ ɔhunu deɛ wɔnhunuu no no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Gyidie na ɔde dii Twam ne mogyapete no, na mmakan no sɛefoɔ no anka wɔn.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Gyidie na wɔde twaa Mmɛwa Po no sɛ fam a awoɔ. Ɛno na Misraimfoɔ resɔ ahwɛ no, ɛmenee wɔn.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Gyidie nti na Yeriko afasuo a wɔtwaa ho hyiaa nnanson no dwiriiɛ.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Gyidie nti na odwamamfoɔ Rahab a ɔgyee akwansrafoɔ no asomdwoeɛ soɔ no ansɛe amfra wɔn a wɔannye annie no mu.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɛdeɛn na menka bio? Na sɛ mereka Gideon, Barak, Samson, Yefta, Dawid ne Samuel ne adiyifoɔ no ho asɛm a, anka adagyeɛ bɛbɔ me.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Wɔn na wɔnam gyidie so ko dii ahennie ahodoɔ so nkonim, dii asɛntenenee, nyinyaa bɔhyɛ, sii agyata ano,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> dumm ogya tumi, dwanee nkrantɛ ano, nyaa ahoɔmmerɛ mu ahoɔden, yɛɛ ɔko mu ahoɔdenfoɔ, kaa ananafoɔ mpasua guiɛ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Mmaa nsa kaa wɔn awufoɔ a wɔasɔreɛ; na ebinom nso, wɔde wɔn goroo atɔprɛ, na wɔampɛ ɔgyeɛ, na wɔn nsa aka owusɔreɛ a ɛyɛ kyɛne soɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na afoforɔ hunuu animguasedeɛ ne ɔhweɛ, mpokyerɛ ne afiase nna nso.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Wɔsii wɔn aboɔ, de sradaa paee wɔn mu, sɔɔ wɔn hwɛɛ, de nkrantɛ kunkumm wɔn. Wɔkyinii nnwanten ne mmirekyie nwoma mu, ɛhiaa wɔn, wɔn ho dwanee wɔn, wɔhunuu amane.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Wɔn a wɔnsɛ wiase, wɔkyinkyinii ɛserɛ so, ne mmepɔ so, abodan ne asase so abɔn mu.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na yeinom nyinaa a wɔnam gyidie so nyaa adanseɛ pa no, wɔn nsa anka bɔhyɛ no,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn asiesie biribi a ɛyɛ kyɛne soɔ asie yɛn, na wɔankwati yɛn anyɛ wɔn pɛ."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saa nti yɛn nso, ɛnam sɛ yɛwɔ adansefoɔ pii a ɛte sɛɛ a atwa yɛn ho ahyia yi, momma yɛnto adesoa biara ne bɔne a ɛnkyɛ na ɛtwa yɛn ho hyia si yɛn kwan no ngu, na yɛmfa boasetɔ ntu akansie a ɛda yɛn anim no mu mmirika,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> nhwɛ gyidie mu kannifoɔ ne ne wiefoɔ Yesu a ɔhwɛɛ anigyeɛ a ɛda n’anim too ne bo ase hunuu asɛnnua amaneɛ, na wammu aniwuo, na wakɔtena Nyankopɔn ahennwa nifa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na monsusu deɛ ɔtoo ne bo ase, tiee ntuatuaano a nnebɔneyɛfoɔ de tuaa n’ano bebree no ho yie, na moammrɛ, na mo kra antɔ piti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mo ne bɔne redi ako yi, monnya nsii ano nkɔduruu mogyahwiegu mu,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na mo werɛ afi afotuo a ɛkasa kyerɛ mo sɛ mma no, sɛ: Me ba, mmu Awurade asotwe ade ketewa, nanso ɔyi wo atɛn a, mma w’aba mu mmu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na deɛ Awurade dɔ no no na ɔtwe n’aso, na ɔhwe ɔba biara a ɔgye no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sɛ mohunu asotwe mu amane tena mu a, Onyankopɔn yɛ mo sɛ mma. Na ɔba bɛn na ɔwɔ hɔ a n’agya ntwe n’aso?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ monni asotwe a wɔn nyinaa anya bie no bi a, ɛnneɛ na moyɛ adwaman mma, na ɛnyɛ mma mapa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bio, yɛwɔ yɛn honam fam agyanom sɛ asotwefoɔ na yɛfɛre wɔn. Adɛn nti na yɛmmfa yɛn ho nhyɛ ahonhom Agya no ase, nkyɛne saa pii mmom, na yɛatena ase?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, wɔtwee yɛn aso nna kakraa bi, sɛdeɛ ɛyɛ wɔ wɔn ani soɔ no nko, na ɔno deɛ, yɛn yie nti na ɔtwe yɛn aso, na yɛanya n’ahoteɛ no bi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na asotwe biara, seesei deɛ, ɛnyɛ yɛn sɛ anigyedeɛ, na mmom awerɛhodeɛ, nanso akyire yi no, ɛso asomdwoeɛ aba a ɛyɛ tenenee ma wɔn a wɔnam so asɔ wɔn ahwɛ no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Enti momma nsa a emu agoɔ ne nkotodwe a ahodwo no mu nyɛ den bio.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na monsiesie ɔkwan tenenee mma mo anan, na deɛ atɔ apakye no antere ho, na mmom wɔasa no yadeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Monni mo ne nnipa nyinaa ntam asomdwoeɛ ne ahoteɛ a obi kwati a, ɔrenhunu Awurade no akyiri.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na monhwɛ yie na obi amfiri Nyankopɔn adom no ho anka akyi, na wannyɛ te sɛ nhini nwononwono bi amfiri anyɛ ɔhaw biara, na wamfa nkekaeɛ ammɛkeka nnipa bebree,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na obi anyɛ odwamamfoɔ anaa ohuhuni sɛ Esau a ɔtɔnee n’abakan gyee aduane korɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na monim sɛ, akyire yi nso a ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔnya nhyira no, wɔpaa no, na ɔde nisuo hwehwɛɛ adwensakyera kwan deɛ, nanso wanhunu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na moamma bepɔ a wɔde nsa ka no ho, ne ogya a ɛrehyeɛ ne mununkum kusuu ne esum ne mframa a ɛbɔ huu",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ne totorobɛnto gyegyeɛ ne nsɛm nne a wɔn a wɔteeɛ no srɛɛ sɛ wɔmmfa asɛm bi nnka wɔn ho bio no ho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔantumi deɛ wɔhyɛeɛ a ɛse: Na sɛ aboa bi mpo ho kɔka bepɔ no a, wɔnsi no aboɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na deɛ ɛpueeɛ no yɛ hu pii nti, Mose kaa sɛ: Mesuro, na me ho popo!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na mmom moaba Sion bepɔ ne Onyankopɔn teasefoɔ kuro, ɔsoro Yerusalem ho, ne abɔfoɔ mpempem nhyiamu,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ne mmakan a wɔatwerɛ wɔn din wɔ ɔsoro no badwa, ne Onyankopɔn, nnipa nyinaa temmufoɔ no, ne ateneneefoɔ a wɔayɛ pɛ ahonhom,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ne Apam Foforɔ ntamgyinafoɔ Yesu, ne mogya a wɔpete a ɛkasa yie sene Habel deɛ ho.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Monhwɛ na moampo deɛ ɔkasa no. Na sɛ wɔn a wɔpoo deɛ ɔkasaa asase soɔ no amfiri ne nsa a, ɛbɛyɛ dɛn na yɛn mmom a sɛ yɛdane firi deɛ ɔfiri soro kasa no ho a, yɛbɛdwane?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɔno na ɛberɛ no mu ne nne wosoo asase, na afei wahyɛ bɔ sɛ: Mɛwoso prɛko bio, ɛnyɛ asase nko, na ɔsoro nso.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na asɛm “prɛko bio” no kyerɛ nnoɔma a wɔwosoɔ no nsakyeraeɛ, sɛ ɛyɛ adeɛ a wɔayɛ, na nnoɔma a ɛnwosoɔ no atena hɔ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Enti ɛnam sɛ yɛanya ahennie a ɛnwosoɔ yi, momma yɛmfa aseda mmra mfa so nsom Onyankopɔn sɛdeɛ ɛsɔ n’ani wɔ fɛreɛ ne ahodasoɔ mu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ yɛn Nyankopɔn yɛ ogya a ɛhyeɛ."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Onuadɔ ntena hɔ daa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ahɔhoyɛ nso, mommma mo ani mmpa so; ɛfiri sɛ yei so na ebinom nam yɛɛ abɔfoɔ hɔhoɔ a wɔn ani nni soɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Monkae nneduafoɔ, sɛdeɛ mo ne wɔn na ɛda afiase, ne wɔn a wɔhunu amane biara, sɛ mo ara nso moda so wɔ honam mu yi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wɔnni awadeɛ ni, ade nyinaa mu, na wɔnngu awadeɛ mpa ho fi; ɛfiri sɛ nnwamamfoɔ ne awaresɛefoɔ deɛ, Onyankopɔn bɛbu wɔn atɛn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mommma sikanibereɛ mmma mo abrabɔ mu, na mo ani nsɔ deɛ mowɔ no; ɛfiri sɛ ɔno ara aka sɛ: Merennya wo, nanso merempa wo da.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɛma yɛde nnamyɛ ka sɛ: Awurade ne me boafoɔ, merensuro. Onipa bɛtumi ayɛ me deɛn?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Monkae mo mpanimfoɔ a wɔaka Nyankopɔn asɛm akyerɛ mo. Monhwɛ wɔn abrabɔ awieeɛ nsua wɔn gyidie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Yesu Kristo te sɛdeɛ ɔteɛ nnora, ɛnnɛ, ɛne daapem nyinaa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mommma nkyerɛkyerɛ ahodoɔ ne nsɛm foforɔ mmfa mo nnkyinkyini, na ɛyɛ sɛ wɔde adom hyɛ akoma den, na ɛnyɛ nnuane a wɔn a wɔdiiɛ no nni ho mfasoɔ biara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yɛwɔ afɔrebukyia a wɔn a wɔsom ntomadan no nni ho kwan sɛ wɔdi ho biribie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na mmoa a bɔne nti ɔsɔfo panin de wɔn mogya kɔ kronkron mu no, wɔhye wɔn afunu nsra no akyiri.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yesu nso, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ɔde ɔno ara ne mogya ate ɔman no ho nti, ɔhunuu amane, kuro no pono akyi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛno nti momma yɛmfiri adi nkɔ ne nkyɛn nsraban no akyiri nkɔsoa n’ahohora.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yɛnni kuro a ɛwɔ hɔ daa wɔ ha, na mmom deɛ ɛbɛba no akyiri kwan na yɛhwehwɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Enti momma yɛmfa ne so mmɔ Nyankopɔn ayeyie afɔdeɛ daa, ɛne anofafa a ɛbɔ no abodin no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yieyɛ ne adekyɛ na mommma mo ani mmpa soɔ, ɛfiri sɛ saa afɔrebɔ no sɔ Nyankopɔn ani.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Montie mo mpanimfoɔ na mommrɛ mo ho ase mma wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn na wɔwɛn mo kra sɛ wɔn a wɔbɛbu ho akonta, na wɔde anigyeɛ ayɛ, na ɛnyɛ ahomeguo; ɛfiri sɛ yei nyɛ mfasoɔ biara mma mo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Mommɔ mpaeɛ mma yɛn; ɛfiri sɛ yɛnim pefee sɛ yɛwɔ ahonim pa, pɛ sɛ yɛbɔ yɛn bra yie nnoɔma nyinaa mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mesrɛ mo ara yie sɛ monyɛ yei, na wɔagyae me ama mo ntɛm pa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na asomdwoeɛ Nyankopɔn a ɔnam daa apam no mogya soɔ, ayi nnwan no hwɛfoɔ kɛseɛ a ɔne yɛn Awurade Yesu afiri awufoɔ mu no,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ɔnsiesie mo adepa biara mu mma monyɛ deɛ ɔpɛ, na ɔmfa Yesu Kristo so nyɛ mo mu ade a ɛsɔ n’ani. Ɔno na animuonyam nka no daa daa. Amen.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Anuanom, mesrɛ mo sɛ, montie afotusɛm yi; ɛfiri sɛ matwerɛ no nsɛm tiaa bi mamane mo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Monhunu sɛ wɔagyaa yɛn nua Timoteo; na sɛ ɔba ntɛm pa a, me ne no bɛba abɛhu mo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Monkyea mo mpanimfoɔ nyinaa ne ahotefoɔ nyinaa. Wɔn a wɔfiri Italia kyea mo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Adom nka mo nyinaa. [Amen.]"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;